Akarere ka Musanze kibutse urubyiruko rwo mu cyari Perefegitura ya Ruhengeri rwishwe muri Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi mu 1994, kuri iki Cyumweru tariki ya 14 Gicurasi 2017. Umuyobozi w’Intara y’Amajyaruguru, Musabyimana Jean Claude, yabwiye urubyiruko ko Jenoside yateguwe n’ubutegetsi bwariho ariko ishyirwa mu bikorwa ku mbaraga ahanini zatanzwe n’urubyiruko. Musabyimana yasabye urubyiruko kutagwa mu mutego wo gushukwa nk’uko byagendekeye urubyiruko rwo mu gihe cya Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi. Ati
