), agira ati “Nk’Abatutsi bahigwaga mu bibi byose twakorewe urubyiruko ni rwo rwari mu b’imbere babikoze; nk’abo bana baturindaga ngo hatagira uca mu rihumye abicanyi bari abana batoya, bakirwa badutuka ngo turi inyenzi, inzoka n’ibindi bitutsi byinshi kandi ubwo uwagerageza gucika ubo bana ni bo bahitaga bamwica.” Nyiraneza Justine, wari ufite imyaka 15 mu gihe cya Jenoside, akaba by’umwihariko yararokokeye ku Mugezi wa Mukungwa uhuza Uturere twa Musanze, Gakenke, Nyabihu na Muhanga agira ati “
